2.3 PollutionRose, percentilRose e polarPlot

library(gridExtra) #plotar figuras juntas

o3_pa <- polarAnnulus(dado, pollutant = "o3", 
             period = "hour", 
             exclude.missing = FALSE,
             key.position = "bottom", 
             key.footer = "O3 (ppb)")

o3_pr <- percentileRose(dado, pollutant="o3", 
                        percentile = 75, 
                        method = "cpf", 
                        col = "blue", 
                        smooth = TRUE)

o3_pp <- polarPlot(dado, pollutant = "o3", 
                    key.position = "bottom",
                    key.footer = "O3 (ppb)")

grid.arrange(o3_pa$plot, o3_pr$plot, o3_pp$plot, nrow=1, ncol=3)

polarAnnulus(dado, poll = "o3", 
             period = "weekday", 
             main = "Weekday",
             key.position = "bottom",
             key.footer = "O3 (ppb)")

2.4 TimeVariation

timeVariation(dado, pollutant = c("nox", "NO", "no2"))

tv <- splitByDate(dado, dates = "1/8/2019", 
                  labels = c("Before Aug. 2019", "After Aug. 2019"))

o3 <-timeVariation(tv, pollutant = c("o3"), 
                            group = "split.by", 
                            ylab = " O3 (ppb)", 
                            xlab = c("Hour", "Hour", "Month", "Weekday"),
                            ylim = c(0,70))

plot(o3, subset = "hour")

print(o3, split = c(1, 1, 1, 2), subset = "hour")
